\fs55\fsmilli27648 \cf2 \cb3 Think hard about the possible future directions of the companies you are examining and determine how current waves of change could build on themselves to produce lollapalooza effects. ResMed, the sleep apnea device manufacturer mentioned earlier, is a good example to consider. With an aging population, increasing obesity (and apnea) rates around the world, and products that are both safe and effective, it is no wonder this company is enjoying success. Multiple factors working in unison can produce amazing results!\cb1 \
